{"tid":1816330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幸福傷風素成分","createTime":"2020-01-08T07:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T09:43:38.000Z","uid":73915,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"79f1709a7a9c0cb46288c12924121b5429aa51c1","tid":1816330,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"都係普通料，藥房全部有售<br />\n跟返份量就ok<br />\n<br />\n（必理痛）Paracetamol (Acetaminophen) 250mg<br />\nPurpose: Relieves pain &amp; fever<br />\n<br />\n（收鼻水）Chlorpheniramine Maleate 2mg<br />\nPurpose: Relieves allergic symptoms such as runny nose, sneezing, watery eyes and itchy eyes<br />\n<br />\n（通鼻塞）Phenylephrine Hydrochloride 5mg<br />\nPurpose: Relieves nasal congestion and eases breathing<br />\n<br />\n（維他命B1）Thiamine Hydrochloride (Vitamin B1) 3mg<br />\nPurpose: Promotes carbohydrate metabolism and maintains normal functioning of the cardiovascular, nervous and digestive systems<br />\n<br />\n（咖啡恩）Caffeine Anhydrous 30mg<br />\nPurpose: Improves wakefulness and relieves tiredness caused by cold &amp; flu"},{"pid":"02c8a25e6a931b513b3c5c46ca5a1b2db0ba0416","tid":1816330,"uid":321674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b65452a283916ba99f1a74d2a2b13972e558e563","tid":1816330,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:33:32.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"9e3bab124f7b98e2bba852631cdd8fb5b99db0a1","tid":1816330,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"原來有咖啡因咁仆街"},{"pid":"e3fa4499acf5c922573f9916079bce462206dc3f","tid":1816330,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3bab124f7b98e2bba852631cdd8fb5b99db0a1","tid":1816330,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"原來有咖啡因咁仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"係咪果d乜鬼無睡意配方? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d